snippet.title: Become the Ultimate Marvel Champion! | Marvel Contest of Champions
snippet.description:
An Elder of The Universe known as The Collector has summoned you to a contest of epic proportions against Marvel super villain Kang The Conqueror.  Experience the ultimate free-to-play fighting game for your mobile device.

Download for free now!

iPhone and iPad: http://bit.ly/1GkZLSq
Android: http://bit.ly/1sdUbR4
